{"tid":2086389,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【病毒進化】新冠病毒進化高清照曝光現「觸手」 向健康細胞注毒製「殭屍細胞」","createTime":"2020-06-30T09:10:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-30T09:37:06.000Z","uid":11148,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"6b9f81c261dfc2c5b39ed6466a6b13c191998f1b","tid":2086389,"uid":11148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T09:10:35.000Z","msg":"新冠病毒被發現已經進化！美國近日有研究發現，<span style=\"color: red;\">新冠病毒會令受感染的人體細胞「殭屍化」，長出帶有病毒、有如「觸手」般的尖刺，去接觸鄰近的健康細胞，並注射「毒液」令病毒擴散</span>。對此，研究人員形容病毒「非常陰險」，但相信新發現有助為新療法打開大門。<br />\n<br />\n綜合外媒報道，研究由美國加州大學（University of California）帶領進行，研究人員透過顯微鏡拍攝的圖片發現，感染病毒的人體細胞會長出有如「觸手」般的「絲狀偽足」（filopodia），上面更布滿帶有「毒液」的病毒顆粒，然後伸向其他健康細胞注入「毒液」，從而製造更多「殭屍細胞」<br />\n受感染的人體細胞會長出「絲狀偽足」，上面更布滿帶有「毒液」的病毒顆粒。（網上圖片）<br />\n<br />\n研究人員指出，新冠病毒目前被普遍認為，其傳播方式與其他病毒一樣，是透過依附在健康細胞後大量複製；而身體健康人士，能透過自身免疫系統擊退大部份病毒。不過，今次研究發現病毒已經進化，<span style=\"color: red;\">已發展出「後備機制」繞過免疫系統</span>。<br />\n<br />\n對此，領導研究的加州大學細胞及分子藥理學教授Nevan Krogan表示：<br />\n<br />\n「<span style=\"color: red;\">這種病毒非常陰險，在殺死細胞前會利用另一機制感染其他細胞</span>。」<br />\n他指出，其他病毒，包括人類免疫缺陷病毒（HIV，又稱愛滋病毒）和牛痘，也使用絲狀偽足作為「播毒」途徑；但新冠病毒能如此迅速地長出「觸手」，則是極不尋常，而且像樹幹般向外伸展的形狀也很奇怪。目前，研究結果已於國際著名學術期刊《細胞》上刊登。<br />\n<a href=\"https://skypost.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2683003/%E3%80%90%E7%97%85%E6%AF%92%E9%80%B2%E5%8C%96%E3%80%91%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E7%97%85%E6%AF%92%E9%80%B2%E5%8C%96%E9%AB%98%E6%B8%85%E7%85%A7%E6%9B%9D%E5%85%89%E7%8F%BE%E3%80%8C%E8%A7%B8%E6%89%8B%E3%80%8D%20%E5%90%91%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%E7%B4%B0%E8%83%9E%E6%B3%A8%E6%AF%92%E8%A3%BD%E3%80%8C%E6%AE%AD%E5%B1%8D%E7%B4%B0%E8%83%9E%E3%80%8D\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fskypost.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Farticle%2F2683003%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E7%2597%2585%25E6%25AF%2592%25E9%2580%25B2%25E5%258C%2596%25E3%2580%2591%25E6%2596%25B0%25E5%2586%25A0%25E7%2597%2585%25E6%25AF%2592%25E9%2580%25B2%25E5%258C%2596%25E9%25AB%2598%25E6%25B8%2585%25E7%2585%25A7%25E6%259B%259D%25E5%2585%2589%25E7%258F%25BE%25E3%2580%258C%25E8%25A7%25B8%25E6%2589%258B%25E3%2580%258D%2520%25E5%2590%2591%25E5%2581%25A5%25E5%25BA%25B7%25E7%25B4%25B0%25E8%2583%259E%25E6%25B3%25A8%25E6%25AF%2592%25E8%25A3%25BD%25E3%2580%258C%25E6%25AE%25AD%25E5%25B1%258D%25E7%25B4%25B0%25E8%2583%259E%25E3%2580%258D&d=r9GgQvVcrWtMp%2Fshn5VX%2FzX0Nqj3uEASyejP0bzfnYY%3D&h=5cbf9e8c\" target=\"_blank\">https://skypost.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2683003/%E3%80%90%E7%97%85%E6%AF%92%E9%80%B2%E5%8C%96%E3%80%91%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E7%97%85%E6%AF%92%E9%80%B2%E5%8C%96%E9%AB%98%E6%B8%85%E7%85%A7%E6%9B%9D%E5%85%89%E7%8F%BE%E3%80%8C%E8%A7%B8%E6%89%8B%E3%80%8D%20%E5%90%91%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%E7%B4%B0%E8%83%9E%E6%B3%A8%E6%AF%92%E8%A3%BD%E3%80%8C%E6%AE%AD%E5%B1%8D%E7%B4%B0%E8%83%9E%E3%80%8D</a><br />\n<br />\n好撚勁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47fbd0553e1436c30afeb8cbf46316e63b4b99de","tid":2086389,"uid":11148,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T09:11:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://resource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2680000/2683003/co300620202_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2680000%2F2683003%2Fco300620202_600.jpg&h=845295c4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a481565e49c4b00ae69cba7bc7fd7080233a3c7","tid":2086389,"uid":47614,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T09:11:40.000Z","msg":"抵讚 晴報就幫手貼文貼圖<br />\n<br />\n下次link都唔使擺"},{"pid":"19abae987478fcf975958df6b22464dafdcad448","tid":2086389,"uid":11148,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"4a481565e49c4b00ae69cba7bc7fd7080233a3c7","tid":2086389,"uid":47614,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T09:11:40.000Z","msg":"抵讚 晴報就幫手貼文貼圖<br />\n<br />\n下次link都唔使擺"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T09:13:11.000Z","msg":"唔係話一定要放link咩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"616c3